CBRE is excited to offer, for lease, 222 Governor Road, Braeside.

The property is exceptionally located with main road exposure to Governor Road and is adjacent to the soon to be opened Mordialloc Freeway.

Convenient access to Boundary Road connects the property to nearby major arterials including Springvale Road, Dingley Bypass, Dandenong Bypass & Eastlink.

Property features include:
+ Total floor area: 1,084sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 921sqm*
+ Dual level corporate office of 163sqm*
+ Total building area: 1,084sqm*
+ 3 phase power
+ One (1) container height roller door
+ Ample on-site parking
+ Minutes from Mordialloc Bypass on/off ramps
+ Main road exposure to Governor Road; retail potential with thousands of cars passing daily
+ Easy access to nearby amenities including cafes, shops & Moorabbin DFO

Please enquire for building plans and private inspections.

Exceptionally well built Office/Warehouse with an attention to detail that will always set it apart from its competition.
The building, which is near new totals 1807sqm*

* 849sqm* of 'Grade A' office over two levels
* 958sqm* of high clearance warehouse
* Land area 2,427sqm*

The office area over two levels is in part fully fitted out and can be occupied as a whole or as 3 separate tenancies. The warehouse areas (available in two separate areas if required) features access via (2) container RSD, internal warehouse amenities and mezzanine areas. Other features of the property are the double glazed solar rated glass, a 22,000 litre underground water storage tank, 30 car spaces and a modern architectural design.

Located in the new Governor Road Estate, the property provides excellent access to the Melbourne CBD via Nepean Highway, Boundary & Springvale Roads and also to the Peninsula via the Frankston Freeway. This location is be greatly enhanced by the new EastLink Freeway and the Dingley Bypass.
